### Call Matrix API — example requests (VS Code REST Client / similar)
@base = http://localhost:3000
@token = paste_jwt_here

### Health
GET {{base}}/health

### Login (returns token + user)
POST {{base}}/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "admin@example.com",
  "password": "your-password"
}

### User profile (any authenticated role)
GET {{base}}/user/profile
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Update profile name
PATCH {{base}}/user/profile
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "name": "New Name"
}

### Admin: dashboard aggregates
GET {{base}}/admin/dashboard
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Admin: create SaaS user (canonical + legacy alias)
POST {{base}}/admin/users/create
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "name": "John Doe",
  "email": "john@company.com",
  "company": "Acme Inc",
  "plan": "pro"
}

### Admin: create user (legacy alias)
POST {{base}}/admin/create-user
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "name": "John Doe",
  "email": "john2@company.com",
  "company": "Acme Inc",
  "plan": "pro"
}

### Admin: list users
GET {{base}}/admin/users
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Admin: patch user (name, company, plan, status, role)
PATCH {{base}}/admin/users/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "plan": "enterprise",
  "status": "active"
}

### Admin: delete user (canonical)
DELETE {{base}}/admin/users/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Admin: create additional API credential for user
POST {{base}}/admin/credentials/create
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "user_id": "00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000"
}

### Admin: list credentials (add ?includeRevoked=true for all)
GET {{base}}/admin/credentials
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Admin: revoke credential
DELETE {{base}}/admin/credentials/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Admin: regenerate API keys for user
POST {{base}}/admin/api/regenerate
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "user_id": "00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000"
}

### Admin: platform agents / campaigns / calls
GET {{base}}/admin/agents
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

GET {{base}}/admin/campaigns
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

GET {{base}}/admin/calls?from=2026-01-01T00:00:00.000Z&to=2026-12-31T23:59:59.999Z
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Admin: analytics
GET {{base}}/admin/analytics
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Admin: system logs
GET {{base}}/admin/logs?page=1&limit=20
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Admin: platform settings
GET {{base}}/admin/settings
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

PATCH {{base}}/admin/settings
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "apiLimits": { "requestsPerMinute": 2000 }
}

### Admin: disable user
PATCH {{base}}/admin/user/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000/status
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "status": "disabled"
}

### Admin: reset password (returns new temporary password)
POST {{base}}/admin/user/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000/reset-password
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Admin: usage analytics
GET {{base}}/admin/usage
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Admin: usage with date range (optional)
GET {{base}}/admin/usage?from=2026-01-01T00:00:00.000Z&to=2026-12-31T23:59:59.999Z
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Tenant: create agent (role must be "user")
POST {{base}}/agents/create
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "agentName": "Support Bot",
  "prompt": "You are a helpful assistant.",
  "voice": "alloy",
  "language": "en-US"
}

### Tenant: list agents
GET {{base}}/agents
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Tenant: delete agent
DELETE {{base}}/agents/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Tenant: create campaign
POST {{base}}/campaign/create
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "campaignName": "Q1 outreach",
  "agentId": "00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000"
}

### Tenant: list campaigns
GET {{base}}/campaigns
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Tenant: start / stop campaign
POST {{base}}/campaign/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000/start
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

POST {{base}}/campaign/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000/stop
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Tenant: call logs
GET {{base}}/calls
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

GET {{base}}/calls?campaignId=00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000&from=2026-01-01T00:00:00.000Z&to=2026-12-31T23:59:59.999Z
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
